name: Kaia Gerber
description:
Kaia Jordan Gerber (born September 3, 2001) is an American model and actress. She is the daughter of supermodel Cindy Crawford and businessman Rande Gerber.

Trained on 1.5 base model but examples are from Consistent Factor and Analong Madness

All images were take from SFW images of her modelling and instagram career, post turning 18. (All images are from the last 2 years. She is currently 21)

Please let me know if you have any suggestions/criticism/comments/or requests for the next model, please leave a comment.
